The QNX_CONFIGURATION environment variable should point to the
QNX configuration directory, which should contain the license
and the qconfig directories.

The license directory is where the license is to be found.

The qconfig directory should contain an xml file for the particular GUI.
The xml file should contain the location of the IDE (base),
the host and target for the IDE.

The host and target for command line is defined in the
QNX_HOST and QNX_TARGET environment variables.

