To reset an eval board:
  vi /vws/peg/mv64360_eval/boards/boards_in_use
  find the line with your login name
  take note of the console server IP and port number
  delete that line
  telnet into the console server (172.22.86.22), pw rHoz
  go to priveleged mode (enable)
  clear line # (# is determined by port number.  Eg. port 2004 => line 4)
  ctrl-], quit the telnet session

Alternatively, you can use the eval_con options.  Do a
  eval_con -h
to list all the options.


