Application Profiling

- add "-finstrument-functions" option to compile command line
- add "-lprofilingS" option to link command line after the objects (.o files)

On QNX prompt, start the program like this:
- QPROF_START=1 QPROF_FILE=/tmp/my_prog.ptrace my_prog &

Can embedded profiling info to the kev file (system profiling):
- QPROF_KERNEL_TRACE=1 my_prog &
- tracelogger -d -n 32

